# Copy to .env.local and fill in. Vite exposes VITE_* vars to client code.
#
# Stadia Maps API key for the "Terrain" (Stamen shaded-relief) basemap.
# Optional: without it the app still has the no-key "Topographic" terrain
# option, and Stadia works key-free on localhost. For production, either set
# this OR allowlist your domain in the Stadia dashboard (recommended for a
# static site, since any embedded key is visible in the bundle). If you do
# embed a key, restrict it to your domain in the Stadia dashboard.
VITE_STADIA_API_KEY=
